{
  "stem": "15028.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would-- I don't know if I have a message of-- of my thoughts-- I mean, the way I see things-- I believe about the state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The life is not worth living if God [NON-ENGLISH] we should be Jews and go [NON-ENGLISH] Hitler [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Europe, the United States, Africa, South America, Far East.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Jews cannot live by the state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The way I see it, it's not worth living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If we were to have a state of Israel in 1939 and we could open up doors 6 million Jews-- women and children-- wouldn't have gone for [NON-ENGLISH] just on account they're Jewish.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's my look on it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I-- I believe on it very strongly that Jews can only enjoy the United States, the freedom.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism isn't there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They don't like-- the Gentile world doesn't like us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The anti-Semitism is in the United States and it's in Germany today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it's even in the countries where there is no Jews.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So therefore we Jews and the-- and the-- and all over the world have to see, like the Italians, like the Danish, like the Swedes, we're different.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we have to see to have a strong country, a Jewish state.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "If we don't have a Jewish state, I say it to my children and my grand grandchildren-- our life is not worth living.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm repeating it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Gentile world would never, never recognize a state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Only have they killed 6 million Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They recognized.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And even now, they are trying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They're envious.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They're looking to destroy us-- to destroy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is my message.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I thank you ever so much.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
